<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - BookMyHotel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <%- include("navbar.ejs") %>

        <div class="about-section">
            <h1>About BookMyHotel</h1>
            <p>BookMyHotel is an online platform that simplifies the process of booking hotel accommodations worldwide. It offers a user-friendly interface to compare prices, read reviews, and make reservations effortlessly. With a wide range of options from budget to luxury hotels, BookMyHotel caters to diverse traveler needs. Additionally, it often features special deals and discounts, making it a convenient choice for both leisure and business travelers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feedback-form" id="d">
            <h1>Tell us your feedback.</h1>
            <div class="feedback">
                <img src="/images/feedback.png" alt="">
                <form action="" method="post">
                    <input type="text" name="" placeholder="Your name">
                    <input type="text" class="styled-input" name="" placeholder="Your feedback">
                    <input type="text" name="" placeholder="Rating(out of 5)">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send feedback</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include("footer.ejs") %>

    </div>
    
</body>
</html>